description.en: PaintSwap Finance has the premier open NFT Marketplace on Fantom. It has a unique and sustainable yield farming AMM platform where 50% of farming rewards are locked for 3 months in the Art Gallery. The first project to create a video game built on the Fantom network, as well as many other exciting features in the works.
